=== Internal Form and Function

- **Nutrition**:
  - **Digestive System**: Foregut (mouth, esophagus, crop, gizzard), Midgut (stomach, gastric ceca), Hindgut (intestine, rectum, anus).
  - **Feeding Habits**: Phytophagous (herbivores), Saprophagous (dead animals), Predaceous, Parasitic (including Hyperparasitism and Parasitoids).

