=== Insects and Human Welfare

- **Beneficial Insects**:
  - Pollination (coevolution with plants).
  - Products (honey, silk, shellac).
  - Predators/Parasitoids of pests.

#figure(
  image(images.at("figure-21-34").path, width: 80%),
  caption: images.at("figure-21-34").caption
)

- **Harmful Insects**:
  - Crop pests (defoliators, borers, suckers).
  - Disease vectors (Mosquitoes - Malaria, West Nile; Fleas - Plague; Lice - Typhus).
  - Property destruction (termites, clothes moths).

#figure(
  image(images.at("figure-21-35").path, width: 80%),
