)

- **Control**:
  - Insecticides (issues: resistance, environmental persistence).
  - Biological Control (pathogens, predators, sterile males).
  - Integrated Pest Management (IPM).

=== Classification and Phylogeny

- **Orders**: (Examples shown in figures)
  - Ephemeroptera (Mayflies), Odonata (Dragonflies), Orthoptera (Grasshoppers), Hemiptera (Bugs), Coleoptera (Beetles), Lepidoptera (Butterflies/Moths), Diptera (Flies), Hymenoptera (Bees/Wasps/Ants), etc.

